## Dependency Notice

This project calls [Ollama](https://ollama.com/) as a runtime dependency for
model inference. Ollama is not distributed with this software — it must be
installed and run separately.

This project's MIT license applies solely to the Node.js wrapper code in this
repository and does not extend to Ollama or any other dependency.
